			"body": "Thanks for taking this forward and for the detailed explanation. The link to the regression in #14094 really helped clarify what was going on.\r\n\r\nThis feels like a much cleaner approach, especially keeping the error dialog and routing everything back through the existing JS handling. I’m happy with this direction and glad to help test or tweak anything if needed. Appreciate you looping me in as a co-author!",
